{"comments":"Bounding sphere defined by center and radius.\n\n## Proof References\nAll operations correspond to proven theorems in `proofs/Hydrogen/Math/Sphere.lean`:\n- containsPoint_center: center is always contained\n- containsPoint_point: point sphere contains its center\n- intersectsSphere_self: sphere intersects itself\n- intersectsSphere_comm: intersection is symmetric\n- translate_zero: translate by zero is identity\n- scaleRadius_one: scale by 1 is identity\n\n## Three.js Parity\n- set, setFromPoints, setFromBox, clone, copy\n- isEmpty, makeEmpty, containsPoint, distanceToPoint\n- intersectsSphere, intersectsBox, intersectsPlane\n- clampPoint, getBoundingBox, applyMatrix4, translate\n\n## Applications\n- Bounding volume hierarchies\n- Broad-phase collision detection\n- View frustum culling\n- Physics simulation\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Vector","Vec3"],"Vec3"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"tag":"ParensInType"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[111,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Sphere.purs","start":[111,13]},"title":"Sphere"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Sphere"],"Sphere"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[114,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Sphere.purs","start":[114,1]},"title":"eqSphere"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show